# src/lib/lint/ui — UI typed-API lint rule stubs
#
# These files document the three Phase-8 UI lint rules.
# The actual implementation is registered in:
#   src/compiler/90.tools/lint/main.spl
#
# Rules:
#   UI001  ui_no_raw_widget_kind  — no_raw_widget_kind.spl
#   UI002  ui_no_raw_variant      — no_raw_variant.spl
#   UI003  ui_no_raw_theme_name   — no_raw_theme_name.spl
#
# All three rules are wired into Linter.lint_source() and report via
# bin/simple build lint (LintLevel.Warn by default; configurable via
# [lints] in simple.sdn or @allow/@warn/@deny file attributes).
